## Introducing Flow | Lec 41

- Seems to be a counterpart of Typescript for react.
- Easy to slowly introduce to a large scale project. TypeScript also does that some way but yeah.

## Setting up Flow | Lec 42

- `yarn flow`: It autmatically pulls it from node_modules no need to mention in scripts
- npm install -g flow-typed
- flow-typed install

